122
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,880
Come, let me tell you something.

123
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,480
Who…who are you?

124
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,210
Something important, come on!

125
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,600
Xianrong,

126
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:17,280
