00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,320
But he seldom went there.

606
00:34:19,560 --> 00:34:21,020
And I only went there once.

607
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,400
Where is it?

608
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,770
It's at West Fourth Street, No. 45,

609
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,670
Room 204.

610
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,800
What's your plan next?

611
00:34:37,080 --> 00:34:38,960
I know this is very important.

612
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,880
I can't trust others.

613
00:34:41,630 --> 00:34:43,889
I haven't told anybody and didn't leave.

614
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,440
But now,

615
00:34:46,120 --> 00:34:47,840
I have told you about this.

616
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:50,230
I can leave in peace now.

617
00:34:57,680 --> 00:34:58,480
Don't bother.

618
00:34:59,200 --> 00:35:00,460
You have saved my life.

619
00:35:00,760 --> 00:35:02,440
I can't take more benefits from you.

620
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,160
Take it.

621
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:04,840
Look at your wounds

622
00:35:05,320 --> 00:35:05,880
Besides,

623
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:07,680
you will need money in Shanghai.

624
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:11,720
Thank you.

625
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,240
Ms,

626
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,320
I have found out

627
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:21,960
that the Russian

628
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,040
used to rent

629
00:35:23,220 --> 00:35:24,520
a flat in Shunyuan.

630
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,440
Except for his residence,

631
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,700
there is another flat?

632
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,480
Yes.

633
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:33,960
Call up men

634
00:35:34,680 --> 00:35:35,540
to check it out.

635
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:48,620
Take cover!

636
00:39:33,600 --> 00:39:34,240
Shoot!

637
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:09,600
I got the map!

638
00:40:09,600 --> 00:40:10,240
Let's go!

639
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,480
Leave now!

640
00:40:29,080 --> 00:40:29,840
After her.

641
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,500
Go! I'll cover you!

642
00:41:09,680 --> 00:41:10,360
Go help Xie Xiang!

643
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:11,220
I'll cover you!

644
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:55,760
You want this?

645
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:57,120
Give me that,

646
00:41:57,120 --> 00:41:58,180
and I'll let you go.

647
00:41:58,880 --> 00:42:00,680
Get it by yourself if you want it!

648
00:42:55,080 --> 00:42:55,520
Xie Xiang!

649
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,120
Come here!

650
00:42:57,440 --> 00:42:57,880
Let's go!

651
00:42:57,880 --> 00:42:58,360
Now!
